We have an array of templates in our VM portal aside from those on our order form.&lt;br /&gt; See something you want loading? Let us know and we will see if we can arrange it.&lt;br /&gt;

##Billing/Pricing
Initial purchases may be manually reviewed prior to provisioning, otherwise automated; (&lt;90s typically). All prices exclude VAT. We invoice in GBP.
Residents in the EU will be charged MOSS, if you have a EU VAT ID then your charge will be removed. Prices meet $7/m requirements as of 14:31UTC 10/19/2015. PayPal is enabled for this product range; we also can accept Bank Transfer for existing customers.

